      "raw_code": "-- Mart model: refs the staging models so the parent_map/child_map is\n-- non-trivial. Tagged `marts` (set in dbt_project.yml).\nwith combined as (\n    select\n        user_id,\n        cast(null as numeric) as amount\n    from {{ ref('stg_a') }}\n    union all\n    select\n        user_id,\n        amount\n    from {{ ref('stg_b') }}\n)\n\nselect\n    user_id,\n    sum(amount) as total_amount\nfrom combined\ngroup by user_id\n",
